Tags:
  - Life-Love=Ecstasy=Madness
By: Swami Ramdas
---
When the source of immortal joy is opened within us, it flows and saturates
every fibre of our being, internal and external, and makes our life at once a
waveless peace and ceaseless thrill of ecstasy. Death, fear, and grief have
then no significance for us.
